{"tid":2257040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國宣布將加強西太平洋海上巡邏力量  對付中國漁船的“非法活動”","createTime":"2020-10-24T23:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T02:19:38.000Z","uid":204533,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3eddab60d4c51fde96d88ef5e852a46c1483be56","tid":2257040,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白宮國家安全顧問奧布萊恩在周五（10月23日）發表的一份聲明中表示，美國海岸警衛隊將在西太平洋部署新一代的&ldquo;哨兵級（Sentinel）&rdquo;快速反應巡邏艦。<br />\n<br />\n在談到中國漁船活動的時候，這位總統安全顧問稱，它們的活動是&ldquo;非法的&rdquo;、&ldquo;不通報的&rdquo;、和&ldquo;不合規則的&rdquo;，對美國和美國的區域夥伴的主權構成了威脅。<br />\n<br />\n聲明還說，中國海軍經常派出軍艦保護大型捕魚船隊進入印太地區有關國家的專屬經濟區展開作業並進行騷擾，危害了地區穩定和有關國家的主權。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，&ldquo;美國海岸警衛隊將在西太平洋的路易斯安那造船廠為改進型快速反應巡邏艦提供一個戰略性母港。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩說，這些巡邏船將執行海洋安全任務，與&ldquo;那些離岸巡防能力有限的&rdquo;地區夥伴合作，幫助受到威脅的漁船，確保海上航行自由。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n..........<br />\n今年7月，美國國防部長埃斯珀對中國軍隊在南中國軍艦撞沉越南一艘漁船、騷擾馬來西亞開採油氣作業和護送中國漁船進入印度尼西亞專屬經濟區捕魚等惡劣行為進行了強烈譴責。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/tensions-explode-as-us-sends-ships-to-confront-illegal-chinese-fishing-in-pacific-20201024/5634267.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Ftensions-explode-as-us-sends-ships-to-confront-illegal-chinese-fishing-in-pacific-20201024%2F5634267.html&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=6ad4277b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/tensions-explode-as-us-sends-ships-to-confront-illegal-chinese-fishing-in-pacific-20201024/5634267.html</a>"},{"pid":"03378e6bb759ee97969cda5b895fba7eb8883cc4","tid":2257040,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478f8dbc65dd658fbee70aa2627424e41f8e60a2","tid":2257040,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:15:35.000Z","msg":"真。主持公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ef0e135778477ae015019140af136416f98fc1","tid":2257040,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"中國會唔會用漁船去打破美軍不可戰勝神話呢?"},{"pid":"649cb147236720b3aa7f8eda2f61048a032f24ed","tid":2257040,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:40:14.000Z","msg":"即係近岸巡邏艦？<br />\n擺落釣魚台就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff04d63ad43141f39d56e483fd0d671ed4fda48","tid":2257040,"uid":8681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:40:47.000Z","msg":"希望可以見到支那漁船隊全滅"},{"pid":"2b609e1e0b13575be590bf36c33d5697623f8dcb","tid":2257040,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:46:28.000Z","msg":"即係話美國在 西太平洋的巡邏<br />\n是（為了對付中國漁船的）<strong>非法活動</strong>"},{"pid":"7c46ef2fcb7981e9c431e7a7be6a5cfc929e883b","tid":2257040,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94149c5838f8670dea7597cbab75090e598388c4","tid":2257040,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff04d63ad43141f39d56e483fd0d671ed4fda48","tid":2257040,"uid":8681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:40:47.000Z","msg":"希望可以見到支那漁船隊全滅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:54:59.000Z","msg":"跟住中國話你殘殺佢人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b999229109bbe89ca7e634ea06ff94630d962378","tid":2257040,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649cb147236720b3aa7f8eda2f61048a032f24ed","tid":2257040,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T23:40:14.000Z","msg":"即係近岸巡邏艦？<br />\n擺落釣魚台就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hk